{"tid":140442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LiSA(織部里沙)歌迷俱樂部 #2","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T10:38:16.000Z","uid":75215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d004238b43ffce515a36466ad22c48910070db","tid":140442,"uid":75215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/11/173556_67057be138f12cd1a55caeb35b159064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F11%2F173556_67057be138f12cd1a55caeb35b159064.jpg&h=0e2408d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LiSA</span></span></strong><br />\n原名 織部里沙<br />\n6月24日生日<br />\n日本的女歌手，岐阜縣出身，高中時期開始組成「CHUCKY」 <br />\nCHUCKY於2008年解散。後來與Parking Out的成員合併組成樂隊「Love is Same All」，其藝名從該樂隊的隊名縮寫而來。<br />\n2010年為Angel Beats劇中Band「Girls Dead Monster」第二主音ユイ幕後代唱<br />\n2011年4月首次以個人名義推出mini album 正式出道 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[新碟]</span></strong><br />\n劇場版SAO theme song - <span style=\"color: red;\">Catch the Moment</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqEaAE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqEaAE8.jpg&h=323158ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pudLJ-L9ZI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpudLJ-L9ZI8&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a916465c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pudLJ-L9ZI8</a><br />\n<br />\n【日本 ARENA TOUR決定！】<br />\n「LiVE is Smile Always～LiTTLE DEViL PARADE～」<br />\n✯6月17日(土) 神戸ワールド記念ホール<br />\n✯6月24日(土) 25日(日) さいたまスーパーアリーナ <span style=\"color: red;\">(6月24日LiSA正日生日)</span><br />\n✯7月1日(土) 日本ガイシホール<br />\n※先行抽選中: <a href=\"http://www.lxixsxa.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lxixsxa.com%2F&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4e324924\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lxixsxa.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[必睇]</span></strong><br />\nLiVE is Smile Always~LOVER&ldquo;S&quot;MiLE~in日比谷野外大音楽堂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Fw2K2suzcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Fw2K2suzcA&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8d197389\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Fw2K2suzcA</a><br />\n<br />\nLiSA - Rising Hope (魔法科高校的劣等生OP):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzhMzY5avLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIzhMzY5avLI&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=48ff319e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzhMzY5avLI</a><br />\n<br />\n[舊POST]<br />\nLiSA歌迷俱樂部 #1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/74447/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/74447/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ony5W7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ony5W7.jpg&h=6568d76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9Tc73u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9Tc73u.jpg&h=37897373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e535eafad69a71493463370732ba012ba4ba81ed","tid":140442,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"91a00a5e99c6e25d000cdbdbec2a8d7abb773393","tid":140442,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"開錯左台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開番個新既係動漫台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />